  "description": "<b>据彭博社报道，从索尼爱立信转投HTC不到三年的该公司COO马修&#8226;科斯特洛(Matthew&#160;Costello)已经离职。</b>HTC负责工程及运营的总裁刘庆东(Fred&#160;Liu)将接管科斯特洛的工作。据彭博社获取的刘庆东向员工发送的邮件显示，科斯特洛将担任公司的执行顾问。HTC对彭博社问询邮件的回复也证实了这一消息。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2cd29a44/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239883.htm&amp;t=HTC%E5%86%8D%E5%A4%B1%E9%AB%98%E7%AE%A1+%E9%A6%96%E5%B8%AD%E8%BF%90%E8%90%A5%E5%AE%98%E7%A7%91%E6%96%AF%E7%89%B9%E6%B4%9B%E7%A6%BB%E8%81%8C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239883.htm&amp;t=HTC%E5%86%8D%E5%A4%B1%E9%AB%98%E7%AE%A1+%E9%A6%96%E5%B8%AD%E8%BF%90%E8%90%A5%E5%AE%98%E7%A7%91%E6%96%AF%E7%89%B9%E6%B4%9B%E7%A6%BB%E8%81%8C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239883.htm&amp;t=HTC%E5%86%8D%E5%A4%B1%E9%AB%98%E7%AE%A1+%E9%A6%96%E5%B8%AD%E8%BF%90%E8%90%A5%E5%AE%98%E7%A7%91%E6%96%AF%E7%89%B9%E6%B4%9B%E7%A6%BB%E8%81%8C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239883.htm&amp;t=HTC%E5%86%8D%E5%A4%B1%E9%AB%98%E7%AE%A1+%E9%A6%96%E5%B8%AD%E8%BF%90%E8%90%A5%E5%AE%98%E7%A7%91%E6%96%AF%E7%89%B9%E6%B4%9B%E7%A6%BB%E8%81%8C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239883.htm&amp;t=HTC%E5%86%8D%E5%A4%B1%E9%AB%98%E7%AE%A1+%E9%A6%96%E5%B8%AD%E8%B